Discovery, Edcon Medical Funds to Merge, Financial Mail Says

-- B y   J a n a   M a r a i s
-- 
2011-08-03T11:58:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-03/discovery-edcon-medical-funds-to-merge-financial-mail-says.html
Discovery Holdings Ltd. (DSY) ’s health-
insurance unit will merge with the medical insurance fund of
Edcon Holdings (Pty) Ltd. by Jan. 1, adding more than 11,000
members and beneficiaries to Discovery,  Financial Mail  reported.  Discovery shareholders approved the merger in June, the
Johannesburg-based magazine said, citing Discovery spokesman
Duke Malan. Discussions to merge  Bonitas ,  South Africa ’s third-
largest medical insurer, and  Pro Sano  are at an early stage,
Financial Mail said, citing Monwabisi Gantsho, registrar of the
Council for Medical Schemes.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jana Marais in Johannesburg at 
 jmarais@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Viljoen at 
 jviljoen@bloomberg.net  